typeMap

protected Map<String,ResponseMetadata.TypeMetadata> typeMap
Map of metadata for each response type. Map key is the string value of the ResponseType object (eg "SVG") rather than the ResponseType enum object itself to facilitate use in PropertyModel such as PropertyModel(responseMetadata, "type.SVG.preferred")
